  "value": "<p>We operate our own roasteries, one on every continent we cover, from where we distribute right to the <a href=\"https://example.com\" data-new-window=\"true\" title=\"Example link to shops\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">shops</a>. This allows you to experience every cup as if you were right at the very farm it originated from. To achieve this, we use a refurbished 1920s Probat coffee roasters.</p>\n<figure data-image-id=\"14mio\"><img src=\"https://assets-us-01.kc-usercontent.com/38af179c-40ba-42e7-a5ca-33b8cdcc0d45/237362b4-5f2b-480e-a1d3-0ad5a6d5f8bd/roaster.jpg\" alt=\"Roasting coffee beans\" data-image-id=\"14mio\"></figure><p>We know that roasting is something you must keep on constantly perfecting. <object type=\"application/kenticocloud\" data-type=\"item\" data-rel=\"component\" data-codename=\"n249afaaf_1de5_011f_f683_c78fd9ec9d7c\"></object> Each coffee requires a different roast to get the aroma and taste just right. That’s why our experts fine tune the way we <a data-item-id=\"f4b3fc05-e988-4dae-9ac1-a94aba566474\" href=\"\">roast coffees</a> every day. It’s a constant struggle.</p><object type=\"application/kenticocloud\" data-type=\"item\" data-codename=\"coffee_processing_techniques\"></object>"
}

